high_descs: Turn left and then left again to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick the knife up from the counter.
Put the knife down on the bread.
Slice the bread on the counter.
Pick up the piece from the counter.
Go left and face the fridge to the right.
Put the bread in the fridge and close the door and then open the door and take out the bread.
Go to the right to face the counter to the right of the fridge.
Put the bread on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled bread on the counter.

high_descs: Walk left and turn to your left to face the kitchen counter
Pick up a knife off of the kitchen counter
Use the knife to slice the bread on the kitchen counter
Put the knife down on top of the sliced bread
Pick up a slice of bread off of the kitchen counter
Walk to your left and turn to your right to face the fridge
Open the fridge door and put the slice of bread in the fridge to chill for a few seconds before taking it out and closing the door
Turn right and immediately turn to face your left
Put the slice of chilled bread down on the kitchen counter
anns.task_desc: Slice some bread, chill it and put it down on a kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn to the left, walk forward turn to face the counter top.
Pick up the knife behind the bread on the counter top.
Move the bread forward on the counter top.
Cut the end of the bread with the knife, place the knife on the bread.
Pick up the slice of bread.
Turn to the left, walk forward, turn to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the slice of bread beside the potato. Close the door then open the door and pick up the slice of bread.
Turn right then face the counter top to the left of the stove.
Place the bread on the counter top between the pan and the knife on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Slice the bread with the knife, place the bread in the refrigerator, move it to the counter top by the stove.
